{"title": "Lorelei Death", "description": "A Space Siren - luring spacemen to their doom with beauty and irresistible call. Chip Warren and his crewmates are celebrating when a fatal shooting interrupts their plans. Chip and his companions must face The Lorelei in order to clear themselves. Intrigue and themes of morality, along with the appropriate use of new technologies, add a hint of romance and you have a suspenseful space adventure! (Summary by Cindy Morton)", "duration": 5592, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "9804", "name": "Nelson S. Bond"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_2603.jpg", "copyright_year": "1941", "genres": ["Science Fiction"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "cyndajm"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "cyndajm"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Ann Boulais"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "Lynette Caulkins"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "I", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_01_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1142}, {"section": 2, "title": "II", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_02_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 897}, {"section": 3, "title": "III", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_03_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 758}, {"section": 4, "title": "IV", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_04_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1147}, {"section": 5, "title": "V", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_05_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 737}, {"section": 6, "title": "VI", "readers": [20206], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/loreleideath_2603_librivox/loreleideath_06_bond_64kb.mp3", "duration": 911}]}